OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1781770692
OL,3,CMan jailed for life for murdering
OL,4,Cmother of three
OL,6,FA 31-year-old Southsea man has been
OL,7,Fjailed for life, with a minimum term
OL,8,Fof 17 years, for murdering his
OL,9,Fpartner, Samantha Murphy, in
OL,10,FPortsmouth last year.
OL,12,FCharlie James Jeans of Margate Road in
OL,13,FSouthsea appeared at Portsmouth Crown
OL,14,FCourt on Wednesday 17 June, after
OL,15,Fchanging his plea mid-trial and
OL,16,Fadmitting his guilt.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
