FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1781770692
OL,3,CMan jailed for life for murdering
OL,4,Cmother of three
OL,6,FOfficers were called at 7:37am on
OL,7,FThursday 5 June 2025, to a report that
OL,8,Fthe body of 32-year-old Samantha had
OL,9,Fbeen located at her address on Wadham
OL,10,FRoad in Portsmouth.
OL,12,FFollowing an investigation by the
OL,13,FMajor Crime team, officers identified
OL,14,FCCTV which showed that Samantha and
OL,15,Fher partner, Jeans, had been at a pub
OL,16,Ftogether until around 11:30pm on
OL,17,FWednesday 4 June.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1781770692
OL,3,CMan jailed for life for murdering
OL,4,Cmother of three
OL,6,FDoorbell camera footage from Wadham
OL,7,FRoad then captured them walking in the
OL,8,Fdirection of Samantha's address, and a
OL,9,Fnotification found on Samantha's phone
OL,10,Fshowed an activation of her own
OL,11,Fdoorbell camera at around 11:45pm.
OL,13,FA neighbour reported that a short time
OL,14,Flater, they heard a loud voice
OL,15,Fshouting "I'm going to kill you", and
OL,16,Fthen a woman screaming.
OL,26,@wD@JOUwD@`O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/13
