PN,38504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1781770692
OL,3,CMan jailed for life for murdering
OL,4,Cmother of three
OL,6,FAt around 12:20am on Thursday 5 June,
OL,7,FJeans sent a text message to his
OL,8,Fmother telling her, 'I'm going to
OL,9,Fprison for a very long time I love
OL,10,Fyou'.
OL,12,FJeans was then seen on the doorbell
OL,13,Fcamera leaving the address at 1:40am,
OL,14,Fafter which he went into hiding for
OL,15,Ffour days, until being located and
OL,16,Farrested.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1781770692
OL,3,CMan jailed for life for murdering
OL,4,Cmother of three
OL,6,FJeans initially pleaded not guilty to
OL,7,Fmurder and appeared at Portsmouth
OL,8,FCrown Court last week for trial, but
OL,9,Ffive days in, on Monday 15 June, he
OL,10,Fchanged his plea and admitted to
OL,11,Fmurdering Samantha.
OL,13,FThis afternoon, Wednesday 17 June,
OL,14,FJeans was sentenced to life
OL,15,Fimprisonment with a minimum term of 17
OL,16,Fyears.
OL,18,FSamantha's family and friends,
OL,19,Fspeaking outside of court after the
OL,20,Fhearing, said, "Today, we have secured
OL,21,Fjustice for our beautiful Sammie Jo.
OL,26,@|D@POU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1781770693
OL,3,CMan jailed for life for murdering
OL,4,Cmother of three
OL,6,F"Sam was a kind and loving daughter,
OL,7,Fsister, and mother. To me, she was my
OL,8,Fbest friend and sidekick.
OL,10,F"To her sisters, Louise & Jodie, she
OL,11,Fwas a deeply beloved friend and baby
OL,12,Fsister. Her contagious laugh lit up
OL,13,Fevery room, and she was adored by all
OL,14,Fwho met her.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1781770693
OL,3,CMan jailed for life for murdering
OL,4,Cmother of three
OL,6,F"Above all, Sam was a fiercely devoted
OL,7,Fmother to her three young children.
OL,8,FThey were her world. We are united in
OL,9,Four promise to give them the love,
OL,10,Fcare, and support they need to thrive.
OL,11,FWe will ensure they grow up knowing
OL,12,Fexactly how much their mother adored
OL,13,Fthem.
OL,15,F"From the beginning, we were
OL,16,Fdetermined to see justice done.
OL,17,FReaching this milestone allows us to
OL,18,Ffocus entirely on celebrating Sam's
OL,19,Flife, and we will never allow the
OL,20,Flight she brought to us all to be
OL,21,Fforgotten.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1781770693
OL,3,CMan jailed for life for murdering
OL,4,Cmother of three
OL,6,F"We extend our deepest thanks to
OL,7,FHampshire Constabulary and Jo Martin
OL,8,FKC for her unwavering support and
OL,9,Fdedication. Shine bright, Sammie."
OL,11,FSenior Investigating Officer,
OL,12,FDetective Chief Inspector Jody
OL,13,FBeresford said, "Samantha's life was
OL,14,Fcut cruelly short by a man who she
OL,15,Fshould have been able to trust and
OL,16,Frely on.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@bO]uD@QOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1781770693
OL,3,CMan jailed for life for murdering
OL,4,Cmother of three
OL,6,F"Jeans betrayed her in a way that most
OL,7,Fpeople cannot even imagine. In one
OL,8,Fselfish, violent act, he has robbed
OL,9,FSamantha of her future and her family
OL,10,Fand friends of their loved one.
OL,12,F"Whilst I am glad to see Jeans put
OL,13,Fbehind bars, today my thoughts remain
OL,14,Fsolely with those who knew and loved
OL,15,FSamantha. Murder is a crime that no
OL,16,Fsentence will ever truly bring justice
OL,17,Ffor.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1781770693
OL,3,CMan jailed for life for murdering
OL,4,Cmother of three
OL,6,F"I'd like to thank Samantha's family
OL,7,Ffor their support throughout this
OL,8,Finvestigation. I can only imagine how
OL,9,Fdifficult the last year has been for
OL,10,Fyou all, but your assistance has been
OL,11,Finvaluable in seeing today's result
OL,12,Fsecured.
OL,14,F"I would also like to thank my
OL,15,Finvestigation team, who's relentless
OL,16,Fhard work and dedication left Jeans
OL,17,Fwith no choice but to admit his guilt
OL,18,Fand face the consequences."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/13
